<div class="alert text-dark fw-bold shadow alert-info text-center mx-auto my-5 mb-4" 
style="max-width: 600px; font-size: 0.9rem;">
    <strong>🚀 Supported Platforms:</strong> TikTok, Instagram, Facebook, Reddit, Twitch, & SoundCloud. 
