                <button class="accordion-button collapsed fw-bold text-dark rounded-4" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faqCollapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faqCollapseThree">
                    What formats are supported for extraction?
